<text xml:lang="ta" type="edition">
  <body>
    <div rend="parallel">
      <lg xml:id="NMT82">
<l>kalantāṉeṉ ṉuḷḷattuk kāmavēḷ tātai</l>
<l>nalantāṉu mītoppa tuṇṭē yalarntalarka</l>
<l>ḷiṭṭēttu mīcaṉum nāṉmukaṉu meṉṟivarkaḷ</l>
<l>viṭṭētta māṭṭāta vēntu.</l>
      </lg>
      <lg xml:lang="en">
<l>The father of Kāma, the King—whom Śiva, the four-faced [Brahmā],</l>
<l>and the like, who [seek to] extol [Him] placing blossoming flowers,</l>
<l>cannot extol [Him by] expressing [themselves]—</l>
<l>became absorbed in my heart. Is there a goodness equal to this?</l>
      </lg>
    </div>
  </body>
